                <div class="row center-aligned-row">
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <h1>{% trans %}TREE PROPAGATION{% endtrans %}</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6 cover-text">
                        <p>{% trans %}ATP has learned how to successfully plant<br>
                            over 50 varieties of trees and shrubs across<br>
